        </div>
    </article>
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
</section>
<section class="about">
    <article>
        <h2 class="fadein">About us</h2>
        <p class="fadein">Welcome to ِAbby exotic Furniture, where luxury furniture meets artistic excellence. We specialize in crafting exquisite gold-plated designs that redefine opulence. With meticulous attention to detail and a commitment to timeless elegance, each piece in our collection is a true masterpiece. Indulge in the allure of our luxurious creations and elevate your living spaces to unparalleled levels of sophistication. Experience the epitome of luxury living with ِAbby exotic Furniture.</p>
        <a href="about-us" class="--button _white fadein" aria-label="button page about us">
            <partial name="Assets/Emogy" />
            <span>About Us</span>
        </a>
    </article>
</section>
<section class="service">
    <article>
        <div class="service-info fade-left">
